      I copy and pasted the test data into its own file, using the IDE itself.
	  Then I opened the 'WatchWindowDisplay.razor' dialog that shows all the values.

LeftVirtualizationBoundary:
	WidthInPixels: 0
	HeightInPixels: 690
	LeftInPixels: 0
	TopInPixels: 0

RightVirtualizationBoundary:
	WidthInPixels: -1600
	HeightInPixels: 690
	LeftInPixels: 2000
	TopInPixels: 0

